  <description><![CDATA[<p>Opening December 2016 located in the heart of the old village of Alpe d'Huez, this attractive brand new stone and wood-clad chalet building encompasses Chalets Grande Fontbelle and Petite Fontbelle. With a shared hot tub and sauna, these chalets are an exciting addition to our chalets in Alpe d'Huez. Chalet Grande Fontbelle takes up the first and second floors with a superb open-plan living dining area with open fire, picture windows and a balcony. The seven bedrooms are all stylishly decorated and some have balconies- all have their own en suite shower rooms. For ski access, the nearby 'Telecentre' ski lift will take you directly to the foot of the main ski lifts and at the end of the day you can ski to within 150m of the chalet.</p>]]></description>
